high_descs: Turn left, go straight ahead a small bit and enter the door on the right to the kitchen, going towards the diningtable.
Pick up the potato from the table.
Turn towards the fridge on the right.
Place the potato into the fridge, let it cool and remove it.
Place the potato on the diningtable near the teapot.
anns.task_desc: Cool a potato in a fridge and place it on a dining table.

high_descs: Open the door and place the potato on the third level. Close the door and wait 5 seconds. Open the door and take the potato. Close the door.
Place the potato to the right of the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Find a potato, cool it and then place it on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Take the potato in the dining table
The potato moves towards the fridge
Open the fridge put it to the potato and take it again
Place the potato on the dining table
anns.task_desc: Pick the potato from the dining table  put the potato in fridge place the potato on the dining table
